OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784033312
OL,3,CFour-year-old girl dies after
OL,4,Ccollision in Nottinghamshire
OL,6,FA child has died following a collision
OL,7,Fwith a car in Gotham, in
OL,8,FNottinghamshire.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FNottingham Road at 2.28pm on Sunday 12
OL,12,FJuly. The four-year-old girl died a
OL,13,Fshort time later in hospital.
OL,15,FA 59-year-old man was arrested on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of causing death by
OL,17,Fdangerous driving. He has been
OL,18,Fquestioned and bailed.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
