OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1784033312
OL,3,CFour-year-old girl dies after
OL,4,Ccollision in Nottinghamshire
OL,6,FSergeant Paul Clark said: "This is a
OL,7,Fdeeply tragic incident and our
OL,8,Fthoughts are with the young girl's
OL,9,Floved ones at this unimaginably
OL,10,Fdifficult time.
OL,12,F"The circumstances are being
OL,13,Finvestigated and we would ask people
OL,14,Fnot to speculate on social media. I
OL,15,Fwould also ask the privacy of the
OL,16,Ffamily is respected as they come to
OL,17,Fterms with what has happened.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
