OL,3,CFour-year-old girl dies after
OL,4,Ccollision in Nottinghamshire
OL,6,FThe investigation is being led by
OL,7,Fofficers in the Serious Collision
OL,8,FInvestigation Unit who are appealing
OL,9,Ffor witnesses and anyone driving in
OL,10,Fthe vicinity at the time who may have
OL,11,Fcaptured footage on dash cam, to
OL,12,Fcontact them.
